The <span style="color: #700000;">**КПГ**</span> поддерживает своего кандидата, их выбор: [+ kpd_candidate +]. [? if kpd_relation >= 50 : Убедить их, им нужен: [+ spd_candidate +]; как нам их убедить? ?][? if kpd_relation < 50 or kpd_leader != "Conciliators" : Похоже, их не убедить. ?]

- @kpd_resources: Использовать наши ресурсы.
- @kpd_relations: Использовать наши хорошие отношения.
- @r1_menu: Забыть о <span style="color: #700000;">**КПГ**</span>.
- @r2_campaigning: Забыть о <span style="color: #700000;">**КПГ**</span>.


@kpd_resources
view-if: kpd_relation >= 50 and not historical_mode
choose-if: resources >= 3
subtitle: -3 ресурса
unavailable-subtitle: Недостаточно ресурсов (нужно 3).
on-arrival: resources -= 3; kpd_candidate = spd_candidate; sapd_candidate = spd_candidate;
go-to: r1_menu if round = 0; r2_campaigning if round > 0

Теперь выбор <span style="color: #700000;">**КПГ**</span> на президентских выборах: [+ spd_candidate +]! Мы просим их не афишировать свою поддержку, чтобы не оттолкнуть буржуазных избирателей.


@kpd_relations
view-if: kpd_relation >= 60 or (kpd_leader == "Conciliators" and kpd_relation >= 45)
unavailable-subtitle: Наши отношения недостаточно хороши.
on-arrival: kpd_candidate = spd_candidate; sapd_candidate = spd_candidate;
go-to: r1_menu if round = 0; r2_campaigning if round > 0

Теперь выбор <span style="color: #700000;">**КПГ**</span> на президентских выборах: [+ spd_candidate +]! Мы просим их не афишировать свою поддержку, чтобы не оттолкнуть буржуазных избирателей.


@convince_dvp_unity
title: Убедить <span style="color: #C0A054;">**ННП**</span>: им нужен [+ spd_candidate +].
unavailable-subtitle: <span style="color: #C0A054;">ННП</span> не желает поддерживать нашего кандидата.
view-if: (spd_candidate = center_candidate_1934 or spd_candidate = lib_candidate_1934 or spd_candidate = "Eckener") and dvp_candidate != spd_candidate and not lvp_formed and dvp_exist
choose-if: dvp_relation >= 40
on-arrival: dvp_candidate = spd_candidate
go-to: r1_menu if round = 0; r2_campaigning if round > 0
max-visits: 1

[? if dvp_candidate = spd_candidate: Благодаря нашим хорошим отношениям и тому, что наш кандидат — единый и не связан с <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span>, the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**ННП**</span> удалось убедить: [+ spd_candidate +] теперь и их кандидат. ?]


@round_1
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: post_election




@post_election
on-arrival: {!
var candidate_descs = {
Hitler: "Adolf Hitler of the <span style='color: #7A3C00; font-weight: bold;'>NSDAP</span>",
Goring: "Hermann Göring of the <span style='color: #7A3C00; font-weight: bold;'>NSDAP</span>",
Seldte: "Franz Seldte of the <span style='color: #3E88B3; font-weight: bold;'>Stahlhelm</span>/<span style='color: #3E88B3; font-weight: bold;'>DNVP</span>",
Hergt: "Oskar Hergt of the <span style='color: #3E88B3; font-weight: bold;'>DNVP</span>",
Eckener: "the independent <span style='color: #000000;'>rep</span><span style='color: #DD0000;'>ubl</span><span style='color: #FFCC00;'>ican</span> candidate Hugo Eckener",
Adenauer: "Konrad Adenauer of the <span style='color: #000000;'>Center Party</span>",
Bruning: "Heinrich Brüning of the <span style='color: #000000;'>Center Party</span>",
Lettow_Vorbeck: "Lettow-Vorbeck of the <span style='color: #000000; font-weight: bold;'>CVP</span>",
Gessler: "Otto Gessler, independent formerly of the <span style='color: #D3C24D; font-weight: bold;'>DDP</span>",
Heuss: "Theodor Heuss of the <span style='color: #D3C24D; font-weight: bold;'>DDP</span>",
Thalmann: "Ernst Thälmann of the <span style='color: #700000; font-weight: bold;'>KPD</span>",
Munzenberg: "Willi Münzenberg of the <span style='color: #700000; font-weight: bold;'>KPD</span>",
Braun: "Otto Braun of the <span style='color: #c00000; font-weight: bold;'>SPD</span>",
Schumacher: "Kurt Schumacher of the <span style='color: #c00000; font-weight: bold;'>SPD</span>",
Juchacz: "Marie Juchacz of the <span style='color: #c00000; font-weight: bold;'>SPD</span>",
Einstein: "Albert Einstein, scientist",
Mann: "Heinrich Mann, writer",
Ossietzky: "Carl von Ossietzky, journalist"
}
if (Q.z_party_name == "CVP") {
    candidate_descs.Adenauer = "Konrad Adenauer of the <span style='color: #000000; font-weight: bold;'>CVP</span>";
    candidate_descs.Bruning = "Heinrich Brüning of the <span style='color: #000000; font-weight: bold;'>CVP</span>";
}
if (Q.lvp_formed) {
    candidate_descs.Heuss = "Theodor Heuss of the <span style='color: #FFCC00; font-weight: bold;'>LVP</span>";
}

if (typeof Q.last_round_candidates === 'undefined') {
    Q.last_round_candidates = [];
}

var candidate_votes = {};
var current_round_candidates = [];

for (var k in candidate_descs) {
    Q[k + '_running'] = 0;
}
for (var i = 0; i < Q.parties.length; i++) {
    var party = Q.parties[i];
    var supported_candidate = Q[party + '_candidate'];
    //console.log(party, supported_candidate);
    supported_candidate = supported_candidate.normalize("NFD").replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, "");
    if (supported_candidate == "Lettow-Vorbeck") supported_candidate = "Lettow_Vorbeck";
    Q[supported_candidate + '_running'] = 1;
    if (!current_round_candidates.includes(supported_candidate)) {
        current_round_candidates.push(supported_candidate);
    }
    if (supported_candidate in candidate_votes) {
        candidate_votes[supported_candidate] += Q[party+'_normalized'];
    } else {
        candidate_votes[supported_candidate] = Q[party+'_normalized'];
    }
}
var total_votes = 0;
Q.winner = "";
Q.winner_votes = 0;
Q.has_majority = 0;

if (Q.Center_bonus && Q.center_candidate_1934 in candidate_votes) {
    Q[Q.center_candidate_1934 + '_bonus'] = Q.Center_bonus;
}

if (Q.Liberal_bonus && Q.lib_candidate_1934 in candidate_votes) {
    Q[Q.lib_candidate_1934 + '_bonus'] = Q.Liberal_bonus;
}

if (Q.Reactionary_bonus && Q.reactionary_candidate_1934 in candidate_votes) {
    Q[Q.reactionary_candidate_1934 + '_bonus'] = Q.Reactionary_bonus;
}

for (var k in candidate_votes) {
    if (Q[k + '_bonus']) {
        candidate_votes[k] += Q[k + '_bonus']/100;
    }
    total_votes += candidate_votes[k];
    if (candidate_votes[k] > Q.winner_votes) {
        Q.winner = k;
        Q.winner_votes = candidate_votes[k];
    }
    if (candidate_votes[k] >= 0.5) {
        Q.has_majority = 1;
    }
} 

for (var k in candidate_votes) {
    Q[k + '_votes'] = Math.round(1000*candidate_votes[k]/total_votes)/10;
    Q[k + '_votes_disp'] = Q[k + '_votes'].toFixed(1);
}

for (var lastCandidate of Q.last_round_candidates) {
    if (!current_round_candidates.includes(lastCandidate)) {
        delete Q[lastCandidate + '_votes'];
        delete Q[lastCandidate + '_votes_disp'];
    }
}

Q.last_round_candidates = current_round_candidates;

Q.winner_votes = Math.round(1000*Q.winner_votes/total_votes)/10;
Q.winner_votes_disp = Q.winner_votes.toFixed(1);
Q.winner_desc = candidate_descs[Q.winner];

if (Q.Braun_votes || Q.Schumacher_votes || Q.Juchacz_votes) {
    Q.spd_running = 1;
    if (Q.Braun_votes_disp) Q.Socialist_votes_disp = Q.Braun_votes_disp;
    if (Q.Schumacher_votes_disp) Q.Socialist_votes_disp = Q.Schumacher_votes_disp;
    if (Q.Juchacz_votes_disp) Q.Socialist_votes_disp = Q.Juchacz_votes_disp;
} else {
    Q.spd_running = 0;
}


if (Q.Gessler_votes || Q.Heuss_votes) {
    Q.lib_running = 1;
    if (Q.Gessler_votes_disp) {
        Q.Liberal_votes = Q.Gessler_votes;
        Q.Liberal_votes_disp = Q.Gessler_votes_disp;
    }
    if (Q.Heuss_votes_disp) {
        Q.Liberal_votes = Q.Heuss_votes;
        Q.Liberal_votes_disp = Q.Heuss_votes_disp;
    }
} else {
    Q.lib_running = 0;
}

if (Q.Adenauer_votes || Q.Bruning_votes) {
    Q.center_running = 1;
    if (Q.Adenauer_votes_disp) {
        Q.Center_votes = Q.Adenauer_votes;
        Q.Center_votes_disp = Q.Adenauer_votes_disp;
    }
    if (Q.Bruning_votes_disp) {
        Q.Center_votes = Q.Bruning_votes;
        Q.Center_votes_disp = Q.Bruning_votes_disp;
    }
} else {
    Q.center_running = 0;
}

if (Q.Hergt_votes || Q.Seldte_votes || Q.Lettow_Vorbeck_votes) {
    Q.reactionary_running = 1;
    if (Q.Hergt_votes_disp) {
        Q.Reactionary_votes = Q.Hergt_votes;
        Q.Reactionary_votes_disp = Q.Hergt_votes_disp;
    }
    if (Q.Seldte_votes_disp) {
        Q.Reactionary_votes = Q.Seldte_votes;
        Q.Reactionary_votes_disp = Q.Seldte_votes_disp;
    }
    if (Q.Lettow_Vorbeck_votes) {
        Q.Reactionary_votes = Q.Lettow_Vorbeck_votes;
        Q.Reactionary_votes_disp = Q.Lettow_Vorbeck_votes;
    }
} else {
    Q.reactionary_running = 0;
}

if (Q.Hugenberg_votes) {
    Q.hamster_running = 1;
} else {
    Q.hamster_running = 0;
}

Q.round += 1
!}
go-to: r2_start if round = 1 and not has_majority; election_end if round > 1; r1_winner if has_majority

Результаты выборов: 

[? if Hitler_running : <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**Гитлер**</span> - [+ Hitler_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if Goring_running : <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**Геринг**</span> - [+ Goring_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if hamster_running : <span style="color: #003755;">**Гугенберг**</span> - [+ Hugenberg_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if reactionary_running and not cvp_formed : <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**[+ reactionary_candidate_1934 +]**</span> - [+ Reactionary_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if reactionary_running and cvp_formed : <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ reactionary_candidate_1934 +]**</span> - [+ Reactionary_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if Thalmann_running : <span style="color: #700000;">**Тельман**</span> - [+ Thalmann_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if Munzenberg_running : <span style="color: #9B0000;">**Мюнценберг**</span> - [+ Munzenberg_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if center_running : <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ center_candidate_1934 +]**</span> - [+ Center_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if lib_running : [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ lib_candidate_1934 +]**</span> ?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**[+ lib_candidate_1934 +]**</span> ?] - [+ Liberal_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if Eckener_running : <span style="color: #000000;">**Эк**</span><span style="color: #DD0000;">**кен**</span><span style="color: #FFCC00;">**ер**</span> - [+ Eckener_votes_disp +]% ?]

[? if spd_running : <span style="color: #c00000;">**[+ spd_candidate +]**</span> - [+ Socialist_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if Einstein_running : <span style="color: #CFC88F;">**Эйнштейн**</span> - [+ Einstein_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if Ossietzky_running : <span style="color: #E0A0A0;">**Осецкий**</span> - [+ Ossietzky_votes_disp +]% ?] [? if Mann_running : <span style="color: #E0A0A0;">**Манн**</span> - [+ Mann_votes_disp +]% ?]


@r2_start
on-arrival: {!
// 1. coordination between the right/far-right
if (!Q.cvp_formed) {
    if (Q.Hitler_votes && Q.Reactionary_votes) {
        if (Q.Hitler_votes > Q.Reactionary_votes) {
            Q.dnvp_candidate = "Hitler";
            Q.other_candidate = "Hitler";
            if (Q.kvp_candidate == Q.reactionary_candidate_1934) Q.kvp_candidate = "Hitler";
            Q.dnf_candidate = "Hitler";
            Q.Hitler_bonus = (Q.Hitler_bonus || 0) - 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            if (Q.center_running) {
                Q.Center_bonus = (Q.Center_bonus || 0) + 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            } else if (Q.lib_running) {
                Q.Liberal_bonus = (Q.Liberal_bonus || 0) + 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            }
        } else {
            Q.nsdap_candidate = Q.reactionary_candidate_1934;
            Q.dnf_candidate = Q.reactionary_candidate_1934;
        }
    } else if (Q.Goring_votes && Q.Reactionary_votes) {
        if (Q.Goring_votes > Q.Reactionary_votes) {
            Q.dnvp_candidate = "Göring";
            if (Q.kvp_candidate == Q.reactionary_candidate_1934) Q.other_candidate = "Göring";
            Q.dnf_candidate = "Göring";
            Q.Goring_bonus = (Q.Goring_bonus || 0) - 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            if (Q.center_running) {
                Q.Center_bonus = (Q.Center_bonus || 0) + 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            } else if (Q.lib_running) {
                Q.Liberal_bonus = (Q.Liberal_bonus || 0) + 0.25*Q.other_votes;
            }
        } else {
            Q.nsdap_candidate = Q.reactionary_candidate_1934;
            Q.dnf_candidate = Q.reactionary_candidate_1934;
        }
    }
}
// 2. If Adenauer & Gessler are both running and neither are part of the SPD coalition, the smaller of these drops out.
Q.center_drops_out = 0;
Q.lib_drops_out = 0;
if (!Q.cvp_formed) {
    if (Q.z_candidate == Q.center_candidate_1934 && (Q.ddp_candidate == Q.lib_candidate_1934 && !Q.lvp_formed || Q.dvp_candidate == Q.lib_candidate_1934 && !Q.lvp_formed && Q.dvp_exist || Q.lvp_candidate == Q.lib_candidate_1934 && Q.lvp_formed) && Q.z_candidate != Q.spd_candidate && (Q.ddp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate && !Q.lvp_formed || Q.dvp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate &&   !Q.lvp_formed && Q.dvp_exist || Q.lvp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate && Q.lvp_exist)) {
        if (Q.Center_votes > Q.Liberal_votes) {
            Q.lib_drops_out = 1;
            if (Q.ddp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate) {
                Q.ddp_candidate = Q.center_candidate_1934;
            }
            if (Q.dvp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate) {
                Q.dvp_candidate = Q.center_candidate_1934;
            }
            if (Q.lvp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate) {
                Q.lvp_candidate = Q.center_candidate_1934;
            }
            Q.Center_bonus = (Q.Center_bonus || 0) + 0.25*Q.other_votes;
        } else {
            Q.center_drops_out = 1;
            Q.z_candidate = Q.lib_candidate_1934;
            Q.Liberal_bonus = 0.25*Q.other_votes;
        }
        if (Q.nsdap_candidate == Q.reactionary_candidate_1934) {
            Q.Reactionary_bonus = (Q.Reactionary_bonus || 0) - 0.25*Q.other_votes;
        } else if (Q.nsdap_candidate == "Hitler" || Q.nsdap_candidate == "Göring") {
            Q.Hitler_bonus = (Q.Hitler_bonus || 0) - 0.25*Q.other_votes;
        }
    }
}
// DVP drops out to favor the center candidate
if (Q.dvp_candidate != Q.spd_candidate && Q.dvp_candidate != Q.ddp_candidate && Q.dvp_candidate != Q.z_candidate) {
}
!}
go-to: r2_menu

Лидирует[+ winner_desc +]. В первом туре большинство не набрал никто. Во втором туре кандидат, набравший относительное большинство голосов, одержит победу.

[? if dnvp_candidate = "Hitler" : The <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**НННП**</span> и <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**НСДАП**</span> объединили свои усилия на выборах, и теперь <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**НННП**</span> поддерживает Гитлера во втором туре. Некоторым правым избирателям не нравится такое соглашение, и они могут не принять участие в голосовании. ?] [? if dnvp_candidate = "Göring" : The <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**НННП**</span> и <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**НСДАП**</span> объединили свои усилия на выборах, и теперь <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**НННП**</span> поддерживает Геринга во втором туре. ?] [? if nsdap_candidate = reactionary_candidate_1934 : The <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**НННП**</span> и <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**НСДАП**</span> объединили свои усилия на выборах, и <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**НСДАП**</span> теперь поддерживает[+ reactionary_candidate_1934 +]во втором туре. ?]

[? if lib_drops_out : Кандидат от либералов [+ lib_candidate_1934_disp +] снял свою кандидатуру в пользу [? if z_party_name != "CVP": , кандидата от <span style="color: #000000;">Партии Центра</span> ?][? if z_party_name == "CVP": , кандидата от <span style="color: #000000;">**ХНП**</span> ?]'s [+ center_candidate_1934_disp +]Это консолидирует голоса умеренного «буржуазного блока» и привлекает часть голосов малых правых партий. ?] [? if center_drops_out : The [? if z_party_name != "CVP": , кандидат от <span style="color: #000000;">Партии Центра</span> ?][? if z_party_name == "CVP": , кандидат от <span style="color: #000000;">**ХНП**</span> ?] кандидат [+ center_candidate_1934_disp +] снял свою кандидатуру. Его выбор: [? if not lvp_formed: от <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>[? if dvp_exist: -<span style="color: #C0A054;">**ННП**</span> ?] ?][? if lvp_formed: от <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**ЛНП**</span> ?] кандидата [+ lib_candidate_1934_disp +]. Это консолидирует голоса умеренного «буржуазного блока» и привлекает часть голосов малых правых партий. ?]

Что нам делать?


