- @civil_war: Yes.
- @defeat_democratic: Ещё не поздно бороться конституционными методами.


@defeat_democratic
on-arrival: {!
Q.pro_democracy_votes = Q.spd_votes + Q.ddp_votes + (Q.lvp_votes / 2) + Q.z_votes - (Q.sa_strength*Q.sa_militancy/10) + (Q.rb_strength*Q.rb_militancy/10);
if (Q.pro_republic >= 60) {
    Q.pro_democracy_votes += Q.kpd_votes;
    Q.pro_democracy_votes += Q.dvp_votes;
    Q.pro_democracy_votes += (Q.lvp_votes / 2);
}
!}
go-to: ref_win if pro_democracy_votes >= 50; ref_lose if pro_democracy_votes < 50


@ref_win
on-arrival: constitutional_crisis = 1

Несмотря на угрозы <span style="color: #7A3C00;">нацистов</span>, сторонники <span style="color: #c00000;">**СДПГ**</span> и демократических партий отказались участвовать в референдуме, лишив его необходимого для принятия порога явки. Это небольшая победа, ведь штурмовики по-прежнему бесчинствуют на улицах. Конституционного пути к абсолютной власти не существует, но остановит ли это <span style="color: #7A3C00;">нацистов</span>?

- @game_over: The ending is yet to be seen...


@ref_lose

- @seldte_takes_power: What next?
- @hitler_takes_power: What next?



@election_end
go-to: eckener_win if winner = "Eckener"; juchacz_win if winner = "Juchacz"; bundesrepublik_win if winner = "Schumacher" or winner = "Adenauer"; hitler_victory if winner = "Hitler" or winner = "Göring" or winner = "Goring"; seldte_victory if winner = "Seldte"; hergt_victory_nazi if winner = "Hergt" and nsdap_candidate == "Hergt"; hergt_victory_lite if winner = "Hergt" and nsdap_candidate != "Hergt"; lettow_vorbeck_victory if winner = "Lettow-Vorbeck"; munzenberg_victory if winner = "Munzenberg" or winner = "Münzenberg"; thalmann_victory if winner = "Thalmann" or winner = "Thälmann"; nazis_lose if winner = "Braun" or winner = "Gessler" or winner = "Heuss" or winner = "Bruning"; cultural_victory if winner = "Ossietzky" or winner = "Mann"; einstein_victory if winner = "Einstein"
on-arrival: {!
Q.president = Q.winner;
if (Q.president == "Bruning") Q.president = "Brüning";
if (Q.president == "Thalmann") Q.president = "Thälmann";
if (Q.president == "Munzenberg") Q.president = "Münzenberg";
if (Q.president == "Goring") Q.president = "Göring";

if (Q.president == "Thälmann" || Q.president == "Münzenberg" || Q.president == "Schumacher" || Q.president == "Wels" || Q.president == "Grzesinski" || Q.president == "Juchacz" || Q.president == "Braun" || Q.president == "Ossietzky" || Q.president == "Mann" || Q.president == "Einstein") {
    Q.president_ideology = "Left";
} else if (Q.president == "Eckener" || Q.president == "Adenauer" || Q.president == "Brüning" || Q.president == "Gessler" || Q.president == "Heuss") {
    Q.president_ideology = "Moderate";
} else {
    Q.president_ideology = "Right";
}
!}

На выборах победил [+ winner_desc +].


